headline: Barclays bumps fertilizer maker Mosaic rating on lower volatility in agri market
summary: Investing.com -- Barclays upgraded Fertilizer manufacturer The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) to Overweight from Equal Weight and raised its price target to $33 from $27 saying there is a reduced volatility, cost efficiencies, and growth opportunities in key markets.Mosaic outlined its capital reallocation and growth plans during its investor day on March 18, highlighting expectations for more normalized production costs and expanded market access. Barclays noted that the company’s investments to red
